{
  "stem": "8610.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, it was an example of the sort of frustrations we had to put up with because I was the sort of go-between between the, the Jews, survivors, and the authorities.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had no one else to talk to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another example of the kind of situation we had to put up with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're talking about the Jews of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whilst I was there, I had the opportunity of investigating the situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happens to these people when they come back from concentration camps, go back into civilian life?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Peculiar situation-- in, in Berlin at the time, they had a ruling that they divided-- they supplied people according to a ration scale.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The highest ration scale were called [NON-ENGLISH], the 'victims of fascism.' And they were given a higher rate of scale.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it depended on whether you were fit to labor, to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews who came back were what?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not in a fit state to do heavy manual labor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were put on the lowest possible ration scale.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I wrote to the British officer and commander in Berlin and said, this is unfair.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If anybody is a victim of fascism, it's these people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They should be put on a higher scale.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he, he accepted my message.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But unfortunately, I don't know whether, whether anything transpired because I was only passing through, as it were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I did write to London, pointing out to the Board of Deputies, for example, and pointed out this was the situation, and perhaps it ought to be known.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, these were the sort of things we were up against.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was one memorable occasion which I must remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
